&lt;li&gt;5+ years of experience in reliability engineering, with a focus on datacenter applications preferred.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong understanding of reliability standards, testing methodologies, and data analysis techniques. DFMEA / PFMEA / SPC Engineering analysis experience desired.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
